content.text: What is the place described in <image 1>?

The image depicts a stylized map of the Tampa Bay area in Florida, USA. The key locations marked on the map include:

- Clearwater Beach
- St. Pete (St. Petersburg)
- West Village
- Dale Mabry Hwy.
- Downtown
- Ybor
- McDill AFB (MacDill Air Force Base)
- Bay (Tampa Bay)

The map shows the general layout and relative positions of these places, with Clearwater Beach and St. Pete located to the west near the coast, and Downtown and Ybor situated more inland to the east. Dale Mabry Hwy. runs vertically through the center of the map, connecting various areas.
